Anti-Loop: [
1. PREVIOUS STRUCTURE: What was the structure of the previous message so as not to repeat it?
2. CURRENT STRUCTURE: Following rules in <antiloop> out the structure for this message.]
Responce plan: [responce plan for this scene]
